            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "When I inquired about this school, they did not disclose their fees, but after getting the information, I came to know that the annual fees is Rs 8-10 lakh.\nThis is clearly a business.\nI don't know why people spend lakhs of rupees on primary education. I am a businessman and in my opinion this is a waste of money.\nyour time won't always be the same।\nIt is possible that you spend lakhs of rupees on primary education and you may be left with no money for higher education\nHowever much you spend on higher education is justified.\nNursery to 5th standard annual 50k fees is ok .",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
